Class AbstractMessagePublisher

java.lang.Object
  com.inmobi.messaging.publisher.AbstractMessagePublisher
All Implemented Interfaces:
MessagePublisher
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConsolePublisher, FlumeMessagePublisher, ScribeMessagePublisher
public abstract class AbstractMessagePublisher
extends Object
implements MessagePublisher

Abstract class implementing MessagePublisher interface. Initializes StatsEmitter and StatsExposer with configuration defined in file . If no such file exists, statistics will be disabled.
